CD:
Enter specified folder
For example:
 - cd Bookmarks bar/Folder
 - cd ~/Other bookmarks
 - cd ../Bookmarks bar/Folder
LS:
List contents of current bookmark folder
For example:
 - ls -al
 - ls Bookmarks bar/
 - ls book
TAB:
Manage Chrome tabs
Available actions are:
 - OPEN
 - CLOSE
 - NEW
 - LIST
 - INFO
 - ACTIVATE
For example:
 - tab open Bookmark name
 - tab list
 - tab info
BOOKMARK:
Manage bookmarks
Available actions are:
 - OPEN
 - NEW
 - INFO
 - EDIT
